Veronica Taylor https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Veronica_Taylor 0 Kathleen McInerney (born December 4, 1965), known professionally as Veronica Taylor, is an American voice actress known for her dubbing work in English language adaptations of Japanese anime, in particular for voicing Ash Ketchum in the Pokémon anime for the first eight seasons.
